import React from 'react'
import { View, Text } from 'react-native'
import COLORS from '../../assets/colors/colors'

export default function Item() {
    return (
        <View >
            <View style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS.white, width: '95%', borderRadius: 5, height: 70, }}>

            </View>

            <View style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS.green, width: '100%', borderRadius: 5, height: 70, marginTop: 12 }}>

            </View>
            <View style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS.main, width: '100%', borderRadius: 5, height: 70, marginTop: 12 }}>

            </View>

            <View style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS.alternate, width: '100%', borderRadius: 5, height: 70, marginTop: 12 }}>

            </View>
        </View>
    )
}
